Shows the repo is in a detached HEAD state.
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
.fam C
detached : { <stylings> }
.fam
.fi
.if n .RE
.sp
\fI<stylings>\fP
.RS 4
.RE
.RE
.sp
\fBhead\fP
.RS 4
Shows repo HEAD.
