If specified, output will be truncated or expanded to the width.
.br
If not specified or set to \fBnull\fP, output will take as much space as it needs.
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
.fam C
width : 20
.fam
.fi
.if n .RE
.RE
.sp
truncationMode
.RS 4
Truncation mode. Overrides global \fBtruncationMode\fP
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
.fam C
truncationMode : \*(Aqtail\*(Aq
.fam
.fi
.if n .RE
.sp
VALUES: \fBhead\fP, \fBmiddle\fP, \fBtail\fP
.RE
.sp
\fI<stylings>\fP
.RS 4
.RE
.RE
.sp
\fBignored\fP
.RS 4
Shows that repo has ignored files.
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
.fam C
ignored : { <stylings> }
.fam
.fi
.if n .RE
.sp
\fI<stylings>\fP
.RS 4
.RE
.RE
.sp
\fBinitialCommit\fP
.RS 4
Shows that repo has no prior commits.
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
.fam C
initialCommit : { <stylings> }
.fam
.fi
.if n .RE
.sp
\fI<stylings>\fP
.RS 4
.RE
.RE
.sp
\fBlocked\fP
.RS 4
Shows that repo is in lock state.
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
.fam C
locked : { <stylings> }
.fam
.fi
.if n .RE
.sp
\fI<stylings>\fP
.RS 4
.RE
.RE
.sp
\fBmodified\fP
.RS 4
Shows that repo has modified files.
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
.fam C
modified : { <stylings> }
.fam
.fi
.if n .RE
.sp
\fI<stylings>\fP
.RS 4
.RE
.RE
.sp
\fBnoUpstream\fP
.RS 4
Shows that the current branch has no upstream tracking branch.
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
.fam C
noUpstream : { <stylings> }
.fam
.fi
.if n .RE
.sp
\fI<stylings>\fP
.RS 4
.RE
.RE
.sp
\fBoid\fP
.RS 4
Shows commit hash.
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
.fam C
oid : {
   length : <integer>,
   <stylings>
}
.fam
.fi
.if n .RE
.sp
length
.RS 4
Commit hash length.
.sp
