.SS "COLORS & STYLES"
.sp
\fBfg\fP|\fBbg\fP
.RS 4
Foreground and background colors.
.sp
Basic
.RS 4
Named terminal colors.
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
.fam C
fg : \*(Aqred\*(Aq
bg : \*(AqbrightWhite\*(Aq
.fam
.fi
.if n .RE
.sp
VALUES: \fBblack\fP, \fBred\fP, \fBgreen\fP, \fByellow\fP, \fBblue\fP, \fBmagenta\fP, \fBcyan\fP, \fBwhite\fP, \fBbrightBlack\fP, \fBbrightRed\fP, \fBbrightGreen\fP, \fBbrightYellow\fP, \fBbrightBlue\fP, \fBbrightMagenta\fP, \fBbrightCyan\fP, \fBbrightWhite\fP
.RE
.sp
Extended
.RS 4
256\-color terminal palette.
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
.fam C
fg : \*(Aqext 110\*(Aq
bg : \*(Aqext 255\*(Aq
.fam
.fi
.if n .RE
.sp
VALUES: \fBinteger\fP from \fB0\fP to \fB255\fP
.RE
